Quantum "weirdness" arises from incompatible projections between $\mathcal{O}$ and $\mathcal{I}$ frames.
\end{proposition}

\begin{proposition}[Interpretational Discord]
Disagreements about determinism versus indeterminism reflect attempts to reconstruct the complete space $\mathcal{X}$ from incomplete projections.
\end{proposition}

